{"tid":1746204,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[主線任務] 星期日投完票，大家仲要做受訪師！！","createTime":"2019-11-22T15:35:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T22:52:50.000Z","uid":5477,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1fd4c1b214217937af97b407cf30d2633266b685","tid":1746204,"uid":5477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:35:47.000Z","msg":"記住！今年區議會選舉只有香港研究協會申請做票站調查！佢係一個長期受西環資助嘅親北京調查組織<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">即係星期日所有票站調查訪問得你，都係幫中聯辦配票！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n所以，大家投完票，記住要同調查人員講你投左愛國愛港嘅候選人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>想更有效，就要喺朝早大約8點至11點投票然後愛訪！</strong></span>因為西環多數會根據朝早嘅數據，調動下午義工走去邊區拉票，越多假資訊比到佢哋，佢哋啲義工就會以為嗰區好有勝算，下午放少啲人來拉票！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果你星期一好得閒，更加可以喺唔同票站大廈門口出入多幾次！</strong></span>咁就可以做多幾次票站調查啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c17fec45d16ae0b1d3ec91ad720286b4a5fefbc","tid":1746204,"uid":274149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:39:17.000Z","msg":"我支持柯創盛㗎。公公婆婆要留言祝福你的心水後選人。"},{"pid":"505bd876496e7e08b3982c2a804fb5a948637208","tid":1746204,"uid":5477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:42:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d539a6164714b3cd3f3e4c9c912a398d4e6f2e","tid":1746204,"uid":5477,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:44:39.000Z","m